divs: Sighting DetailsI was traveling back from ontonagon Michigan and decided to stop at the park to go to the bathroom, I ended up taking a picture of the bridge and water . It was about a week later and I was going to send it to a friend a nd I noticed that there is object in the picture. I showed it to some friends and even sent it to a news agency to see if their engineers could bring the object into view.
Summary: i was taking this pic of the bridge/water and never noticed anything nor heard it. I looked at the pic about a week later and noticed something strange, i did send a copy to the local news to see if they could clean it up. Not sure what it is
